EN: Some countries have legal regulations on euthanasia.

ZH: 安乐死是一个备受争议的话题。
EN: Euthanasia is a controversial topic.

ZH: 很多人认为安乐死是对的。
EN: Many people believe euthanasia is right.

ZH: 一些宗教反对安乐死。
EN: Some religions oppose euthanasia.

