EN: For patients with terminal illnesses, euthanasia may be a relief.

ZH: 许多人不清楚什么情况下才可以进行安乐死。
EN: Many people are unsure under what circumstances euthanasia can be performed.

ZH: 要进行安乐死，病人必须签署授权书。
EN: To undergo euthanasia, the patient must sign a consent form.

ZH: 医生会为病人提供安乐死的选项。
EN: The doctor will provide the patient with the option of euthanasia.

