EN: Euthanasia must meet moral and legal standards.

ZH: 有些人支持将安乐死合法化。
EN: Some people support legalizing euthanasia.

ZH: 他的病情已经到了需要考虑安乐死的地步。
EN: His condition has reached a point where euthanasia needs to be considered.

